20
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:30,875
Su!

21
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:33,836
Go!

22
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:45,397
Your Highness

23
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:48,150
I'm afraid Su has perished

24
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:52,670
Dead? Are you sure?

25
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:56,356
