55
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:39,157
A great sword deserves a great warrior! You
don't like it?

56
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:39,837
No

57
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,155
Of course, I do

58
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,196
Then it's yours

59
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:42,912
Thank you

60
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:44,837
